WITH RECURSIVE search_tree(id, in_reply_to_id, path) AS ( SELECT id, in_reply_to_id, ARRAY[id] FROM statuses WHERE id = 111360502703416592 UNION ALL SELECT statuses.id, statuses.in_reply_to_id, path || statuses.id FROM search_tree JOIN statuses ON statuses.id = search_tree.in_reply_to_id WHERE NOT statuses.id = ANY(path) ) SELECT id FROM search_tree ORDER BY path LIMIT 4
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" IN ($1, $2, $3) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
